ingbees@gmail.com](mailto:groundnestingbees@gmail.com)\n>\n> Know: Ground nesting bees (which are typically solitary by nature) are not aggressive. However, social ground nesting wasps can be.\n>\n> Together, we will work to support the native pollinator communities for which we all depend.[ less â†‘](https://inaturalist.ca/projects/ground-nesting-bees-3e6882c0-a112-4ddb-b043-1da25638ce96#)","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/globalbioticinteractions/globalbioticinteractions/issues/1122/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/globalbioticinteractions/globalbioticinteractions/issues/1122/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}